    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Tephritis sahandi sp. nov. (1 – 2) and T. volkovitshi (3): 1. paratype ♀, total view, dorsal. 2 – 3. Wings." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/201982/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.201983>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 – 8. Tephritis sahandi sp. nov., paratype 3. 4. Abdomen, dissected, ventral view. 5. Epandrium, posterior view. 6. Epandrium and hypandrium, lateral right view. 7. Glans of phallus, lateral. 8. Ejaculatory apodeme." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/201983/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.201984>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 17. Tephritis sahandi sp. nov., paratype Ƥ. 9. Abdomen, dissected, ventral view. 10. Abdominal sternites 3 – 6, ventral view. 11. Apex of oviscape and eversible membrane, ventral view. 12. Apex of oviscape and basal half of eversible membrane, dorsal view. 13. Aculeus, ventral view. 14. Same, apex. 15. Spermathecae. 16. Ventral receptacle. 17. Egg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/201984/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.201985>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Host plant: Achillea clypeolata, host of Tephritis sahandi." ;
